Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:07.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:36.49,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.93,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:43.16,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:54.30,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:04.55,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he has that recovery magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.37,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.75,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Stupidsta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:16.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first peasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:19.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,that I, a royal, ever acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:21.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:26.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,defeat that guy, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:35.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw enough at him from the both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:37.63,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,...that weakling, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:40.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:59.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:26.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:31.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:35.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:40.28,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.56,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:43.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:47.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:55.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:58.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:01.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:07.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:13.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.56,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:20.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.96,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.67,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction and Salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, I'm fine now, so please \Njust take care of Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.23,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.36,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if my remaining \Nmagic will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.84,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where's all that energy you just had?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die before I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.12,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.33,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, is the training painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.89,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,When things get rough,\Nremember the faces of those you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:36.39,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,We were born to protect the people \Nof this kingdom that we love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:55.91,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Once we become strong enough to protect\Nthis kingdom, we'll be allowed to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.18,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably make it out first, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.17,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:05.69,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're the strongest \Nout of all of us, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.18,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.42,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:15.04,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Until you get out, too, Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.35,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Let's go see the \Noutside world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.61,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,This is your final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.84,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:38.58,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,The sole survivor will be allowed to go \Noutside as our kingdom's mage warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.28,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse, you'll all be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.04,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.56,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.95,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.70,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.18,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mars is the one who survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.20,flashback,Trainer 2,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's implant him with the magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:02.39,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go ahead and give him\NFana's powers, too, since she was
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.33,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,the last one he killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.43,flashback,Trainer 2,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll finally have the \Nultimate mage warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:17.52,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:21.52,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,because I have extremely powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.68,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Those without magic are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.61,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And the weak will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.36,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:32.95,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.45,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It can't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:41.95,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as naïve as you \Ncannot win against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.81,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:58.10,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,His flame recovery magic should've \Nbeen negated by Asta's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.81,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect opportunity \Nto finish him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.19,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more... Just a little more, \Nand I can break through these restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.31,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:19.18,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what spell I pick from\Nmy grimoire, I won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.75,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.71,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yuno just do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:48.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The spell... has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.97,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Was that magic? What did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There was a little girl, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.75,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.96,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:09.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we've defeated him for sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.99,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.95,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,the characters from that scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.71,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:50.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The dungeon is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.79,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Wind Ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.20,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, take care of Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.44,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:38.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Save him... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,came to conquer this dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:56.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not... to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:11.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a waste to let \Nsomeone that strong die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late! We won't make \Nit out in time. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.59,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:34.08,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa can't use her \NMagic Flower Guidepost right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.67,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Go right. I'll guide us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:45.80,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.41,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:14.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,More coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:15.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:35.77,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've already acknowledged \Nyou as my... as our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.43,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.65,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,...Asta die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.27,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:44.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,...alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.73,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.69,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:28.89,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:38.96,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Man... We sure were lucky \Nthey created a path for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:45.71,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this old man's ultimate \Ntrump card, Hermit's Thick Smoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:50.97,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,they never realized we were \Nclose by the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:56.68,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thank goodness you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.73,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.67,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.57,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.69,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.64,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.43,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.07,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:00.41,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't do that, you wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.29,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.60,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.31,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you awake, Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.57,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.93,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Great work back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:31.32,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I was able \Nto get all this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.86,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Now the people of our kingdom, \Nas well as my daughters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.84,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,will be able to eat delicious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:57.59,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.69,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you go see the world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.11,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,For me... as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.86,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.12,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.62,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.92,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You can actually say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:42.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.39,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! As long as you're okay, Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:58.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable.\NYour recuperative ability is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's resilient, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, Yuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:11.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more than just resilient... ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:15.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry! I didn't have \Nenough magic to fully heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:19.61,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I just did what I could for now, \Nso you probably shouldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,N-No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:26.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.67,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,N-No problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to \Ndie before I got to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:38.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die. Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going \Nto be the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup. Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use my body as a crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? \NIt's not like I'm hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.07,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.73,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.29,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:25.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so ashamed that I didn't acknowledge \Nyou just because you were peasants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:32.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,magnificent Magic Knights \Nof the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:46.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffocating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Four-Eyes... it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.19,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What?! And after I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:20:00.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you were such a good four-eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.68,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.39,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too serious, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:12.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:20.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noelle. Your clothes are all ripped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:28.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.18,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help myself! Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.56,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.40,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:31.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:34.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:42.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:47.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:50.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:52.93,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:06.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:13.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:17.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:23.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
