Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.61,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:45.98,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}So You Can Actually\NSay Things Like That
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.40,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So You Can Actually Say Things Like That.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:50.24,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:55.01,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:58.40,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You can actually say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:01.25,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:05.25,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:07.48,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,She sells seashells by the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.48,0:23:09.35,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:11.92,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,How much wood could a woodchuck chuck \Nif a woodchuck could chuck wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:13.26,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.75,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,She sells... she shells... seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:18.49,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper picked... \Na pick of peckled pippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:20.52,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,How much wood could... \Na woodchuck... chuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:22.77,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:24.52,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.89,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,She sells she shells by the she shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.09,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper pipped a \Npep of pippled peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.96,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,How much wood could a \Nwoodchuck... could... chuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.16,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:37.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! Did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:43.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! We just met the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:46.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 20:\N"Assembly at the Royal Capital."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:51.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 20\N\N{\fs18} Assembly at the Royal Capital
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:49.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Being loud is my magic!
